author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tips for stud walls over concrete…I predrill the pressure treated 2x4 then use a special bit with a Makita hammer drill for the concrete. Then I use 3-1/4 inch Tapcon screws to anchor the bottom plate. The sill seal prevents any moisture from wicking into the 2x4 🔥#studwall #carpentry #bathroomremodel #homerepairtutor
